      "widgets_values": [
        "A high-fidelity, cinematic 3D animation of a futuristic cyber-facility representing a computer's kernel. Inside, multiple glowing holographic workers, representing distinct software processes, are manipulating streams of digital code. Suddenly, thick, transparent force fields drop down, enclosing each worker in a completely isolated, soundproof cube, rendering them unable to see or interact with the others. Above each cube, glowing energy pipes are regulated by automated valves that strictly limit the flow of power and material to each worker. The camera pans smoothly across the securely partitioned, efficiently operating grid under moody neon blue and dark grey lighting. Photorealistic, 8k resolution, dynamic lighting."
